OL,3,CTributes paid to 19-year-old solider
OL,4,Cwho died following training session
OL,6,FA 19-year-old British Army soldier has
OL,7,Fdied following a training session at
OL,8,FCatterick Garrison.
OL,10,FPrivate Harry Johnson has been
OL,11,Fdescribed by the Army as having
OL,12,F"enormous potential", with his
OL,13,Fcommanding officer saying he was "the
OL,14,Fkind of young soldier that the country
OL,15,Fneeds".
OL,17,FHe joined the Army on 13 April 2025,
OL,18,Fand was a member of Bruneval Platoon,
OL,19,FParachute Regiment Training Company
OL,20,Fwithin Second Infantry Training
OL,21,FBattalion.
