OL,3,CTributes paid to 19-year-old solider
OL,4,Cwho died following training session
OL,6,FHe died on 24 July following a
OL,7,Fphysical training session at Vimy
OL,8,FBarracks, Catterick.
OL,10,FOne of his fellow recruits with whom
OL,11,Fhe became good friends, Private Cayden
OL,12,FDalgity, said he often talked about
OL,13,Fhis family and his little sister, and
OL,14,Fwas always on the phone with his
OL,15,Fgirlfriend, Abira.
OL,17,FLieutenant Colonel Ben Jesty,
OL,18,FCommanding Officer, Second Infantry
OL,19,FTraining Battalion, said he and his
OL,20,Fcolleagues are "heartbroken" by the
OL,21,Floss of Pte Harry Johnson.
