OL,3,CTributes paid to 19-year-old solider
OL,4,Cwho died following training session
OL,6,FHe said: "Tipped to be a future P
OL,7,FCompany Champion, he was the kind of
OL,8,Fyoung soldier that the country needs:
OL,9,Ffit, determined, disciplined and
OL,10,Fselfless."
OL,12,F"He was a credit to his friends and
OL,13,Ffamily, to whom we offer our most
OL,14,Fheartfelt condolences at this awful
OL,15,Ftime."
